Reizu to regenerate himself.

144
00:09:42,125 --> 00:09:45,250
Karasu, can you tell me
what happened to Fukuro?

145
00:09:45,333 --> 00:09:46,916
Fukuro is...

146
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:48,000
Huh?

147
00:09:54,541 --> 00:09:56,416
