148
00:09:58,041 --> 00:09:59,916
Huh? Hahh?

149
00:10:00,000 --> 00:10:02,708
Tell me, did Atori do this?

150
00:10:02,791 --> 00:10:04,166
He didn't do this.

151
00:10:04,250 --> 00:10:06,958
[HARUKA] It was someone,
or something else.

152
00:10:07,041 --> 00:10:10,291
Only you have the power
to see multiple dimensions.

153
00:10:10,375 --> 00:10:12,208
By observing each dimension,

154
00:10:12,291 --> 00:10:15,625
they are finalized into
existence and become a reality

155
00:10:15,708 --> 00:10:17,833
in which everyone's
lives and deaths

156
00:10:17,916 --> 00:10:20,125
are played out to their
logical conclusion.

157
00:10:20,208 --> 00:10:24,500
