161
00:10:30,125 --> 00:10:33,625
Tell me. He's not
going to die, is he?

162
00:10:33,708 --> 00:10:37,166
[TOBI] At this rate, because
he's exhausted all of his Reizu,

163
00:10:37,250 --> 00:10:39,416
