169
00:10:50,916 --> 00:10:52,208
And what does it do?

170
00:10:52,291 --> 00:10:54,708
[TOBI] Reizu are the
smallest elementary particles

171
00:10:54,791 --> 00:10:57,041
that compose all matter.

172
00:10:57,125 --> 00:10:59,625
