matter, animate or inanimate,

174
00:11:04,500 --> 00:11:08,333
but I don't think they've been
discovered in this world yet.

175
00:11:08,416 --> 00:11:10,375
Hey, did you
catch that, Miss Yukie?

176
00:11:10,458 --> 00:11:12,666
Oh yes, I understood
every word of it.

177
00:11:12,750 --> 00:11:14,291
Impossible.

178
00:11:14,375 --> 00:11:16,000
Huh?

179
00:11:16,083 --> 00:11:17,708
[MIHO]
What are you doing?

180
00:11:17,791 --> 00:11:20,583
This dimension has a
Reizu convergence point.

181
00:11:20,666 --> 00:11:23,750
I am attempting to locate
the coordinates now.

182
00:11:24,916 --> 00:11:26,250
[YU]
Hmm?

183
00:11:28,333 --> 00:11:29,875
I've located it.

184
00:11:29,958 --> 00:11:33,333
We just have to get
him to this point.

185
00:11:33,416 --> 00:11:36,125
If we take him there, will we
be able to save his life?

186
00:11:36,208 --> 00:11:39,000
Yeah, there's a
very good chance.

187
00:11:51,583 --> 00:11:53,875
I'll kill him,
or I'll die trying.

188
