245
00:15:07,458 --> 00:15:09,416
[UCHIDA]
What? At a time like this?

246
00:15:09,500 --> 00:15:11,000
Come on, they're gettin' away!

247
00:15:11,083 --> 00:15:12,500
Step on it!

248
00:15:12,583 --> 00:15:13,666
Kooriyama!

249
00:15:13,750 --> 00:15:16,041
Oh, just calm down,
Uchida, will ya?

250
00:15:16,125 --> 00:15:18,125
There's nothin'
we can do right now.

251
00:15:18,208 --> 00:15:20,125
[UCHIDA]
Why not?

252
00:15:24,541 --> 00:15:26,375
[YU] I think we
lost them, Miss Yukie!

253
00:15:26,458 --> 00:15:28,750
