00:15:32,250 --> 00:15:34,916
[TOBI] This is the place where
the Reizu is converging.

255
00:15:35,000 --> 00:15:37,041
Really? A place like this?

256
00:15:37,125 --> 00:15:39,083
You gotta hold on, Karasu.

257
00:15:39,166 --> 00:15:41,000
We're almost there.

258
00:15:41,750 --> 00:15:43,000
Huh?

259
00:15:44,166 --> 00:15:45,791
Ah!

260
00:15:45,875 --> 00:15:48,041
[YUKIE]
Blue snow?

261
00:15:52,875 --> 00:15:55,250
Uh... What in the hell was that?

262
00:15:55,333 --> 00:15:58,375
Well, well, well,
the gang's all here...

263
00:15:58,458 --> 00:16:01,083
...with the Dragon Torque.

264
00:16:03,458 --> 00:16:04,666
Hmph.

265
00:16:04,750 --> 00:16:06,708
Even if Karasu
managed to kill Fukuro,

266
00:16:06,791 --> 00:16:08,708
it looks like he won't
be getting away with it,

267
00:16:08,791 --> 00:16:10,375
now will he?

268
00:16:11,458 --> 00:16:13,208
You're wrong, Kosagi.

269
00:16:13,291 --> 00:16:16,083
Karasu isn't the one
who killed Fukuro.

270
00:16:16,166 --> 00:16:18,666
[KOSAGI] I'm sorry but I don't
believe the words of traitors.

271
00:16:18,750 --> 00:16:20,416
[TOBI] We really must
stop this, Kosagi.

272
00:16:20,500 --> 00:16:22,291
[KOSAGI]
Pleading for your life, are you?

273
00:16:22,375 --> 00:16:24,250
How cowardly. In fact,

274
00:16:24,333 --> 00:16:27,500
I couldn't care less about
your pathetic little lies.

275
00:16:27,583 --> 00:16:29,375
Hand over the
Dragon Torque. Now!

276
00:16:29,458 --> 00:16:31,583
No. I will not.

277
00:16:31,666 --> 00:16:32,958
This dimension has
not yet reached

278
00:16:33,041 --> 00:16:34,958
the critical point
like La'cryma has,

279
00:16:35,041 --> 00:16:37,583
so by being in this
dimension the Torque may be

280
00:16:37,666 --> 00:16:40,416
the key to return all worlds
to their original states.

281
00:16:40,500 --> 00:16:43,291
I am not going to
listen to your theories.

282
00:16:43,375 --> 00:16:46,958
I will return to La'cryma
with the Dragon Torque.

283
00:16:47,041 --> 00:16:49,625
[KOSAGI] That is my ultimate
mission as a Dragon Knight.

284
00:16:49,708 --> 00:16:51,000
Ahh...

285
00:16:53,500 --> 00:16:54,833
[KOSAGI gasps]

286
00:17:03,083 --> 00:17:04,500
Atori...

287
00:17:04,583 --> 00:17:07,208
You're hanging out with
this little group now?

288
00:17:07,291 --> 00:17:10,750
Let's hurry. Get him
the light of life.

289
00:17:10,833 --> 00:17:12,416
[TOBI]
Huh? Yes, you're right.

290
00:17:12,500 --> 00:17:13,875
Everyone help me.

291
00:17:15,083 --> 00:17:16,416
[YUKIE]
Who is that person?

292
00:17:16,500 --> 00:17:19,333
[YU] Trust me, you're better off
not knowing, Miss Yukie.

293
00:17:21,916 --> 00:17:23,041
Let's do this.

294
00:17:23,125 --> 00:17:28,916
[ATORI panting]

295
00:17:30,291 --> 00:17:32,333
[TOBI]
Be careful now.

296
00:17:32,416 --> 00:17:35,291
[YUKIE] This guy's a lot
lighter than he looks.

297
00:17:36,250 --> 00:17:39,791
Hyaaaaaarghh!

298
00:17:42,583 --> 00:17:44,833
I don't know who you are,

299
00:17:44,916 --> 00:17:47,708
but I took a vow and
I won't let you pass.

300
00:17:47,791 --> 00:17:49,916
Huh? What happened
to you, Atori?

301
00:17:50,000 --> 00:17:52,125
You're not acting like yourself.

302
00:18:12,000 --> 00:18:13,041
[HARUKA]
Karasu!

303
00:18:13,125 --> 00:18:16,125
[TOBI]
It'll be okay.

304
00:18:16,208 --> 00:18:20,041
What the...?

305
00:18:20,125 --> 00:18:21,250
[YUKIE]
What's happening?

306
00:18:21,333 --> 00:18:24,166
The clouds are
flowing towards us.

307
00:18:32,541 --> 00:18:35,416
[ATORI]
I will not let you pass...

308
00:18:35,500 --> 00:18:37,041
You are pathetic.

309
00:18:37,125 --> 00:18:39,833
Have you forgotten how to
fight as well, Atori?

310
00:18:44,125 --> 00:18:45,625
Please hang on.

311
00:18:45,708 --> 00:18:47,833
Don't die, Karasu.

312
00:18:56,083 --> 00:18:57,083
Geh...

313
00:18:57,166 --> 00:18:59,708
Aw hell, what are
you doing anyway?

314
00:18:59,791 --> 00:19:02,875
You should start practicing
what you preach, old man!

315
00:19:02,958 --> 00:19:05,750
Stop making Haruka suffer!

316
00:19:12,583 --> 00:19:16,000
[ATORI] What are you?
You are not human!

317
00:19:17,291 --> 00:19:19,500
Man, you make me sick.

318
00:19:19,583 --> 00:19:22,250
This is the end of
the Dragon Knights.

319
00:19:36,333 --> 00:19:37,833
This is amazing.

320
00:19:37,916 --> 00:19:40,708
I think it's working.
He's getting better.

321
00:19:46,583 --> 00:19:48,916
What? Ahh!

322
00:19:49,000 --> 00:19:50,875
[YUKIE]
Tobi, are you okay?

323
00:19:52,208 --> 00:19:53,791
This is all my fault.

324
00:19:53,875 --> 00:19:57,250
It's my fault for
seeing that future.

325
00:19:57,333 --> 00:19:58,791
That is not true.

326
00:19:58,875 --> 00:20:02,166
It's impossible to have
a future you cannot choose.

327
00:20:02,250 --> 00:20:03,958
There's no such
thing as destiny,

328
00:20:04,041 --> 00:20:07,208
and no way our future
is laid out for us.

329
00:20:07,291 --> 00:20:11,333
But if... if I decide
to go away with her,

330
00:20:11,416 --> 00:20:13,000
then Karasu will be okay.

331
00:20:13,083 --> 00:20:16,125
You can't do that!

332
00:20:16,208 --> 00:20:18,041
No, don't do it, Haruka!

333
00:20:18,125 --> 00:20:19,333
What are you doing?

334
00:20:19,416 --> 00:20:20,750
Huh?

335
00:20:25,916 --> 00:20:29,916
Why is it that you're the one
who always pisses me off?

336
00:20:30,958 --> 00:20:32,708
No, don't!

337
00:20:35,208 --> 00:20:37,375
Dragon Torque!

338
00:20:37,458 --> 00:20:40,291
Go to La'cryma and
become an illusion!

339
00:20:40,375 --> 00:20:41,666
Haruka!

340
00:20:45,291 --> 00:20:47,166
[KOSAGI]
Such an annoyance.

341
00:20:50,416 --> 00:20:52,208
I promised...

342
00:20:52,291 --> 00:20:56,666
I made her a promise
and I do intend to keep it.

343
00:20:56,750 --> 00:20:58,708
For Sara.

344
00:21:04,791 --> 00:21:06,291
[YU]
Haruka, run!

345
00:21:22,208 --> 00:21:25,583
The Reizu, I've never
seen it like this.

346
00:21:31,625 --> 00:21:33,250
What the hell is that?

347
00:21:33,333 --> 00:21:35,750
[KOORIYAMA]
Have you ever seen that before?

348
00:21:55,916 --> 00:22:00,333
[KARASU] Fukuro...
Are you there, my friend?

349
00:22:02,791 --> 00:22:07,000
Isami, are you with Haruka now?

350
00:22:08,291 --> 00:22:12,291
I'm going to stay
here a while longer.

351
00:22:12,375 --> 00:22:14,291
Please tell her,

352
00:22:14,375 --> 00:22:19,583
that I will protect her
in this dimension.

353
00:22:23,083 --> 00:22:30,458
[KOSAGI panting]

354
00:22:30,541 --> 00:22:31,833
[KUINA]
I warned you before.

355
00:22:31,916 --> 00:22:35,250
I told you I would not allow
unauthorized activity!

356
00:22:54,166 --> 00:22:56,958
Haruka...

357
00:22:58,125 --> 00:22:59,750
Uh-huh.

358
00:23:02,208 --> 00:23:04,541
[TOBI]
The future expands to inifinity,

359
00:23:04,625 --> 00:23:08,958
and I'm postive that we're
allowed to make our own choices

360
00:23:09,041 --> 00:23:11,250
and choose our own destiny.

361
00:23:14,041 --> 00:23:16,416
[HARUKA chuckles]

362
00:23:16,500 --> 00:23:20,083
[HARUKA]
Yeah, that sounds nice.

363
00:24:57,958 --> 00:25:00,291
[HARUKA]
I'm dreaming again...

364
00:25:00,375 --> 00:25:03,916
That summer day's dream.

365
00:25:04,000 --> 00:25:06,375
[YU]
Haruka likes you better!

366
00:25:09,708 --> 00:25:12,416
[HARUKA]
Are they your drawings, Mom?

367
00:25:16,125 --> 00:25:19,791
[ASUKA] So you don't even
wanna talk to me anymore?

368
00:25:19,875 --> 00:25:23,416
[HARUKA]
Next episode, "Memories."

369
00:25:23,500 --> 00:25:25,833
Can you sense his feelings?

